    "29 to reliably classify the survival rates of brain cancer patients.",
    "Based on H &E histopathology images, the model gives survival likelihood ranges across four classes.",
    "The datasets were obtained from the TCGA and a nearby hospital.",
    "They included 450 H &E slides from individuals with various types of brain tumors.",
    "For patients who had survived for 0-6, 6-12, 12-24, and over a year, they took into consideration classifications of four grades."
